{"tid":1754754,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"尖沙咀要人呀!!!","createTime":"2019-11-25T10:17:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T12:55:07.000Z","uid":287028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"352295a5c7d76bef9a7cf14d523ebf86d8d49525","tid":1754754,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:17:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/72tJNs8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F72tJNs8.jpg&h=f05e79e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聲援理大手足！唔好放棄！</span></span><br />\n離開的急救員表示，估計理大校園至少還有20人，部分更出現輕生念頭，據他了解曾有至少5人鎅手自殘，精神狀況令人憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">11月25日 (星期一)<br />\n7:30pm-9pm<br />\n和你唱 為理大同學打氣</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">集合地點:<br />\nA. 紅碪南道花園<br />\nB. 尖沙咀梳士巴利花園<br />\nC. 油麻地眾坊街休憩花園</span><br />\n<br />\n理大手足唔係condom，佢地需要大家支持！要唱到入面嘅手足聽到！<br />\n#聲援 #手足不是condom <br />\n#我哋從來都無放棄你哋<br />\n#唔好同我放棄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vb1SFOf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVb1SFOf.png&h=739e80bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins>和你唱歌單</ins></span></strong><br />\n1. 榮光<br />\n2. Sing Hallelujah to the Lord<br />\n3. Do you hear the people sing<br />\n4. 問誰未發聲<br />\n5. 海闊天空<br />\n6. 光輝歲月<br />\n7. 發現號<br />\n8. 煲底相約"},{"pid":"90b8e30851937f0930ca4342b18debdea3b1a7b7","tid":1754754,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:17:33.000Z","msg":"7點半要人呀!!!"},{"pid":"4add2a48bdbe57fa9fbeb004363fb920b29721c1","tid":1754754,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90b8e30851937f0930ca4342b18debdea3b1a7b7","tid":1754754,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:17:33.000Z","msg":"7點半要人呀!!!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:17:44.000Z","msg":"7點半要人呀!!!"},{"pid":"e4966a4618f62b62f01cf665a00cec3b3edb5bb4","tid":1754754,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:17:45.000Z","msg":"雖然區選拎左389席<br />\n但咁嘅選舉制度下仲比建制狗拎到59席<br />\n只可以叫做小勝<br />\n大家開心完之後抗爭運動都要繼續落去<br />\nPOLY仲有一大班手足畀狗圍緊<br />\n仲有好多手足畀狗拉左畀人告緊<br />\n佢地等緊我地光復香港救佢地出黎<br />\n如果我地區選完就退<br />\n點對得住死左嘅手足<br />\n點對得住為我地擋子彈嘅手足<br />\n點對得住畀狗拉左嘅手足<br />\n所以18區要繼續開花<br />\n黎明行動要日日搞<br />\n組織全港大三罷<br />\n直到光復香港為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a46df748f786e1333fa66366b2665081c4e346e","tid":1754754,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:17:54.000Z","msg":"7點半要人呀!!!"},{"pid":"d651fba8ce97053528fbb9ad3a5f811f7b093bfa","tid":1754754,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:18:21.000Z","msg":"7點半要人呀!!!"},{"pid":"01541a3fe11723d7222a443d09e2bbd1d3ef0923","tid":1754754,"uid":3553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:30:27.000Z","msg":"係九龍塘，有d 塞車<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8de60cadec3fd5ff2281831a05664dff008e37","tid":1754754,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:31:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33203cbfac63e96170d46862993da374cecd23c8","tid":1754754,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:31:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af905f126b6b74c91e6c59440460f6c85d31c5d7","tid":1754754,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:31:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ffb23ab1e1e4a51ebed059288f785e7d681baf88","tid":1754754,"uid":81952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:52:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1dfd705aef782bccb9eb42348af5f9767943761e","tid":1754754,"uid":315880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:56:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c386690cd93b7da7ae165bceb0ce7ca487c5af07","tid":1754754,"uid":3